Given the following program and the variable in complex data type, decompose the it into variables with primary data type.. The program is 
struct c {
  int d : 18;
  int e;
  int f;
  int g;
  int h;
};

struct c i;

int main() {
  struct c l = {24, 6738, 165};
  int m = i.e;
  l.d = m;
  int n = i.h && l.d;
  int o = l.d;
  int p = o | -(l.f && l.d) - n;
  i.g = p;
}
.                 The target to be optimized is `l` is a structure of type `struct c`.
